WEBVTT

1
01:14:12.730 --> 01:14:16.310 
听着 我们明早就离开了
OK, look, we're out of here tomorrow morning,

2
01:14:16.310 --> 01:14:18.020 
不会在见到我们了
you'll never see us again.

3
01:14:18.020 --> 01:14:20.440 
一定有办法解决这事的
There's gotta be something due to work this out.

4
01:14:21.860 --> 01:14:22.930 
不如你们放了他
What if you let him go,

5
01:14:22.930 --> 01:14:24.930 
我给些东西来报答你们
and I give you something to thank you?

6
01:14:26.690 --> 01:14:27.660 
你在贿赂我们
You bribing us?

7
01:14:27.740 --> 01:14:31.600 
当然不是 这是送礼答谢
No. Hell no. A gift. A thank you.

8
01:14:32.400 --> 01:14:34.020 
你要怎么感谢呢
What kind of thank you?

9
01:14:34.920 --> 01:14:38.340 
例如 一笔给予警方的捐款
Like a... You know, donation to the police force.

10
01:14:38.440 --> 01:14:39.540 
给你们的
Youse guys.

11
01:14:40.610 --> 01:14:41.760 
你们想要什么
Whatever you want.

